Cookies
CR uses "cookies" to store, and sometimes to track, information about how you use our websites.
You can manage certain cookies by clicking on the categories in this tool.  You can also set your browser to notify you before accepting cookies or to disable them entirely.  If you choose to block some types of cookies, it may prevent you from accessing certain features and services on our websites.
For more information about cookies, go to our
Cookie Policy
.
These cookies are essential for our digital services to function correctly and cannot be switched off via this tool.  They include cookies necessary to enable members to log in to CR.org, access account information, and use certain features and services available to CR members.
You can learn more about managing cookies on popular browsers by clicking on any of these links
Apple Safari
,
Google Chrome
,
Mozilla Firefox
,
Microsoft Edge
,
Microsoft Internet Explorer
.  If you set your browser to block these cookies some part of our CR.org website may not be accessible to you.
